{"tid":442804,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"葵盛東邨19歲男墮樓昏迷　送院搶救不治","createTime":"2017-10-21T04:19:57.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-21T12:53:32.000Z","uid":901,"like":10,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":26,"replies":[{"pid":"ec20788566d78356f2a7634ec0cf3da2910d063f","tid":442804,"uid":901,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-21T04:19:57.000Z","msg":"葵盛東邨一名青年墮樓重傷送院不治。事發於今(20日)晚上9時45分，一名19歲姓周男子由葵盛東邨盛富樓的高處墮下，倒臥大廈對開地面，陷入昏迷，有人見狀報警。救護車接報到場，將事主送往仁濟醫院搶救，卒傷重不治。警方在現場調查，並聯絡事主兄長了解事件，現場消息指，事主留有遺書，疑因健康有問題，家人指他生前任職武術指導。<br />\n<br />\n求助網站和熱線<br />\n<br />\n香港撒瑪利亞防止自殺會熱線 : 23892222<br />\n<br />\n醫院管理局精神健康專線 : 24667350<br />\n<br />\n東華三院芷若園熱線︰18281<br />\n<br />\n撒瑪利亞會熱線︰28960000<br />\n<br />\n​學友社學生熱線：25033399<br />\n<br />\n社會福利署熱線︰23432255<br />\n<br />\n生命熱線 : 23820000<br />\n事主兄長在現場了解事件。<br />\n<br />\n一日一單<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e93fd21af1a7d166812fcded89625c3b43316712","tid":442804,"uid":6294,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-21T04:20:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e379356b88b097eadc9a087c7cb852f42dc64fb1","tid":442804,"uid":901,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-21T04:25:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e9c89c6e3402d0291aca7f6ab755b4c6296de4bf","tid":442804,"uid":901,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-21T04:25:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ea820924019ee5d5409280f0b871cc2463ae0d19","tid":442804,"uid":901,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-21T04:25:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4a88de482f265cb1f3241beae5543a4745c79e2c","tid":442804,"uid":901,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-21T04:25:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=